| &nbsp;
| &nbsp;
| {{IPA|[sluh]}}
| 'to shoot (perfective)'
| →
| {{IPA|[shluh]}}
| 'to shoot (continuative)'
| {{IPA|(s-''h''-lu<u>h</u>)}}
|-
| &nbsp;
